British nationals in Qatar who are considering leaving should contact their travel operator to make arrangements to do so as soon as possible.
Commercial flights continue to operate from Hamad International airport though many operators have cancelled or reduced routes and all flights are subject to change or cancellation at short notice.
You should check with your airline or travel company for the latest information if you are planning to leave Qatar. For more information check Qatar Airways flights
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
